name: Camp Orbit Wire Express KS Quickdraw
description: Great value in a wire-gate draw, is has a carabiner retention system on the dogbone to keep the rope-end carabiner from shifting or twisting. Fat polyester dogbone is tough and comfortable to grab when projecting.Karstop Evo polyurethane retainer prevents the rope-end carabiner from shifting.Orbit Wire carabiners on each end are great for all styles of climbing.Durable 16mm polyester dogbone is comfortable to hold.
